headline: Rand Paul: Did Nancy Pelosi Receive Monoclonal Antibodies?
author: Jeff Poor
sentences: Friday, during an appearance on FNC’s “Hannity,” Sen. Rand Paul (R-KY) suggested there was a possibility of a double standard for Democratic politicians and the public for receiving monoclonal antibodies.

Comments:
